    "description": "<br>Join the official <strong>Discord server</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ROGUE MACHINES HAVE INVADED</h2>An army of intelligent machines have gone rogue in post-war cities. Your highly skilled 3-man team has been commissioned to pilot the <i>Falconet</i>, an advanced weapons entity, to rescue the humans trapped behind enemy lines. <br><br>On your team you have Bangs the engineer, Spike the navigator, and Flo the pilot of the <i>Falconet</i>. You will need to shoot your way through each retro style level to eliminate enemies… before they eliminate you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >USE WEAPONS IN COMBOS</h2>Rapidly switch between your diverse arsenal of weapons with unlimited ammo to annihilate enemies in satisfying combos.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/ba0e31bdb3536e0012538b5687896985.poster.avif?t=1752320148\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/ba0e31bdb3536e0012538b5687896985.webm?t=1752320148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/ba0e31bdb3536e0012538b5687896985.mp4?t=1752320148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PROGRESS BY SOLVING PUZZLES</h2>Gain access to restricted areas in each level using the <i>Falconet’s</i> 6 different colour-coded weapons and your problem-solving skills to take out enemies and generators.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/f6c53082c885f47c0d2fae4265dae15d.poster.avif?t=1752320148\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/f6c53082c885f47c0d2fae4265dae15d.webm?t=1752320148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/f6c53082c885f47c0d2fae4265dae15d.mp4?t=1752320148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RESCUE HUMAN SURVIVORS</h2>Search out survivors in captured areas and bring back hope to the humans you liberate.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/ea27cb6dd34c21ba2622e343d593ba92.poster.avif?t=1752320148\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/ea27cb6dd34c21ba2622e343d593ba92.webm?t=1752320148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/ea27cb6dd34c21ba2622e343d593ba92.mp4?t=1752320148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RACK UP HIGH SCORES</h2>Beat the records you set as you improve in your gun-wielding skills.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/1172ddbca09872f3b52c9db5f39e8ef3.poster.avif?t=1752320148\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/1172ddbca09872f3b52c9db5f39e8ef3.webm?t=1752320148\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803070/extras/1172ddbca09872f3b52c9db5f39e8ef3.mp4?t=1752320148\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
